Kik is here to stay! We re happy to announce that Kik will be staying in the app store where it has been home to millions of users and billions of conversations over the past 9 years. Thank you for your continued support!
A fix for one of our top crashes Thanks for using Kik!
Squashed a few bugs and fixed a crash Thanks for using Kik!
Fixed an issue where Kik would be stuck on Connecting... Fixed a crash that happened after receiving content in certain cases Thanks for using Kik!
Fixed certain display issues for iPhone X and greater devices Thanks for using Kik!
Fixed a few issues with chat themes Thanks for using Kik
Fixed a few issues around displaying Days on Kik Made some under the hood performance improvements Thanks for using Kik!
Fixed a crash that could have happened when turning on Video Chat Fixed an issue that caused delayed keyboard input when typing after upgrading to iOS 12 Thanks for using Kik!
Fixed a crash that happened when adding people to your group Fixed an issue that prevented you from viewing external content sent in Kik Thanks for using Kik!
Improved behaviour when retrieving your chats after logging in Fixed a crash that could occur when group info was being updated
Fixed an issue where your profile wasn t showing up in the members list of a group Two crashes that occurred in and around group chats have been fixed Thanks for using Kik!

Fixed an issue where the message preview in the chat list wasn t displaying the latest message from the chat Resolved two meddlesome crashes affecting your chat experience no more shall they happen Thanks for using Kik!

Looking for a specific chat Now you can pull down your list of chats and search to find the one you want. Swipe down memory lane! Tap on a photo and swipe left right to see your chat s photos videos and GIFs. Now you can 3D Touch Kik s icon to quickly find friends join public groups and discover bots.

Reorder or remove your installed sticker packs any way you want. Just tap on the gear icon in the Sticker Shop. Blocking or banning is easier: Tap on a profile picture to block ban or promote someone to group admin right from the chat screen.

Public Groups are back! Search by topic to find a group and chat about anything that interests you. We also fixed some reported bugs: Messages should say the correct time they were received instead of Just Now. We added crash fixes for users sending content with no network access. Photos should now appear in the same order as the phone s camera roll.

We re back with a small update to squash some reported bugs: Messages should say the correct time they were received instead of Just Now. Crash fixes for users sending content with no network. Also Video Chat bubbles are bigger and now you can use Bluetooth audio! We love getting your feedback. Please keep it coming!

Video Chat bubbles are bigger and you can now use bluetooth audio! Kik is the best way to chat back and forth in realtime and you can get even more personal with video. When you re chatting one to one or in groups just tap the video icon in the top right.

Kik has a brand new look! We ve made it more fun and easy to use so you can spend less time hunting for photos and GIFs and more time chatting with friends and groups. Now you can: Quickly find friends start groups and discover bots with a menu right on the main Kik page. We made it easier to add your favorite photos GIFs and smileys while you re chatting they re available right under the text field for easy access. Organize your thoughts with redesigned chat bubbles. When you have a lot to say and send several messages in a row they ll now group together. And we ve added lots of bug fixes and improvements to make Kik even better.

FAST PICTURE SHARING Share moments with your friends as they happen. Send something funny embarrassing beautiful whatever! It s all about getting your contacts in on the action instantly and privately with a picture message. SIMPLE GROUP CHAT Easily create groups on the go by adding friends to conversations. Share your weekend plans with your friends at work have a chat with the whole family tell your entire team you re running late for practice etc. Group Chat lets you get the message out to the whole gang in a simple safe and private way. SPEED STABILITY BOOST Since the beginning Kik has been known for its blazing speed and dependable service. That s why we ve tweaked some things under the hood to make Kik even faster and more reliable. You re welcome!
